          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The population of the isomeric states is considered in",
                " nuclei 115In-m   (1/2-)   and   180Hf-m    (8-)    in",
                " photonuclear (gamma,gamma') reactions at giant dipole",
                " resonance energies.  The comparison with the  earlier",
                " published  experimental and theoretical data is made.",
                " The behavior of  the  excitation  function  gives  an",
                " evidence for possible increase of the high-spin state",
                " population in the giant resonance range."
              ]
            }
          ],
